      "level": 2,
      "text": "Key Concepts"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "**Product rule**: Stages with $n_1, n_2, \\ldots, n_k$ choices \n give $n_1 \\times n_2 \\times \\cdots \\times n_k$ total outcomes.",
        "**Sum rule**: Mutually exclusive alternatives are added.",
        "**Permutations**: Ordered arrangements. $n! = n(n-1)\\cdots 1$; \n $P(n, r) = n!/(n-r)!$.",
        "**Combinations**: Unordered selections. \n $\\binom{n}{r} = n!/(r!(n-r)!)$.",
        "**Binomial theorem**: \n $(x + y)^n = \\sum_{k=0}^{n} \\binom{n}{k} x^{n-k} y^k$.",
        "**Inclusion-Exclusion**: \n $|A \\cup B| = |A| + |B| - |A \\cap B|$.",
        "**Pigeonhole**: $n$ items in $k$ bins $\\Rightarrow$ some bin \n has $\\geq \\lceil n/k \\rceil$ items."
      ]
    },
